## Troubleshooting
*   **"Error 403: access_denied"**: You forgot to add the user to the "Test Users" list in Google Cloud (if your app is still in "Testing" mode).
*   **Camera not working**: Ensure your site is served over **HTTPS** (Netlify does this automatically). Camera access is blocked on HTTP.
